latestPosts.caption:
Frayed edges and ink darkened lungi, paired with ripped leather pants, spike studded boots and accessories galore - we knew to expect something truly offbeat when it came to @drench.d_studio doing the Lungi styling challenge. It is a brand founded by @_tri__ste_ and @thisssislit to bring their love for grunge and goth inspired streetwear to the streets of Kochi.

From creating custom merch for artists like @mhrofficial__ and @anohnymouss to being part of edgy, editorial shoots - the founding duo has carved out a niche for Drench'D through the community they have found built through and around the brand.
